  <assign id="1139">
    <name>Connect a Set of Tasks to a Sample Formula Sheet</name>
    <intro>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;In this activity, you will choose from a set of tasks that might be typical for students to be asked to solve, often with the support of a “Formula Sheet.” For the formula sheet to be useful to students who do not know an approach or formula on their
    own, students need to be able to locate and use relevant formulas.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;Use Task #2 and one other task of your choosing from
        &lt;span&gt;&lt;a href="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Middle%20School%20Mathematics%20-%20Short%20Tasks%20-%20Geometry.pdf?time=1688770357322" target="_blank" title="PDF - opens in a new window"&gt;Middle School Mathematics – Short Tasks: Geometry&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For each task:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
        &lt;ul style="padding-top: 10px"&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Complete the task using a few different approaches, ideally in ways you anticipate adult learners might respond correctly or incorrectly. Include images of your work when you submit the assignment.&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Respond to the following:
                &lt;ul style="padding-top: 10px"&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;How might learners use diagrams?&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Are there definitions that need to be utilized?&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;List the formulas learners might find helpful for the task.&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Respond to the following:
                &lt;ul style="padding-top: 10px"&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;What do they need to know and understand about the formulas and the figures or constraints described in the task?&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;For &lt;strong&gt;one&lt;/strong&gt; of the two tasks you did above, respond to the following:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;How might drawing a diagram (or drawing on the given diagram) be helpful in using a formula sheet, such as the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span&gt;&lt;a href="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Sample%20Formula%20Sheet.pdf?time=1688770394199" target="_blank" title="PDF - opens in a new window"&gt;Sample Formula Sheet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;?&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;What might adult learners struggle to connect between the task and the formula sheet?&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions for submitting the assignment:&lt;/strong&gt; Click the ADD SUBMISSION button below. You may then upload a document and pictures of your work. Click SAVE CHANGES to save your work. Click SUBMIT ASSIGNMENT when you are done.&lt;/p&gt;</intro>
